The reason I have done so much research about this, is one it effects &quot;marketing&quot; as a whole no matter what industry you are in. Two I cant believe the logic that they are using to &quot;sell&quot; it to the customer.<br>
<br>
Case in point. You call my company for information on products that YOU are interested in and want information on, you leave your name and number for us to call you back, BUT you are on National DNC. I can not call you back to give you the info you asked for, even though you asked me to and gave me your info. To call you back I would need to spend thousands of dollars to digitally record every incoming message to my office, tell every person &quot;you are being recorded&quot; since it is illegal to tape someone w/o prior knowledge(ie entrapment), then save those recordings in my basement in case you get pissed and say &quot;I never called them!!&quot; or for example your husband / wife calls us and leaves message and we call back and get the other party. Oh shit doom on me, opposite party gets pissed records info, denies calling us, 11k fine. Then, does the consumer get the 11k cash? Nope. Where does it go? You tell me but Im betting the same place the 8k for the list went. Did you get your check? I didnt. To answer questions, I have seen a &quot;Example&quot; bill for the fine. There is not a section for explanation. It says Balance 11k to FTC which is the US Goverment. <br>
<br>
So if there is going to be million and damn sure close to a billion of dollars made off of this, why isnt it going to the consumers who put there name on the list!?! Plus the calls will still come, you will still get pissed, BUT someone in the goverment is getting seriously paid, your landscaper is going out of business, 60k americans got shit canned, the economy will be even more fucked, BUT Good ol George Dub and the &quot;Saviors (spl) of dinner time will get a 10% higher approval rating out of this, AND some people will actually vote for them based upon this one topic in coming elections.<br>
<br>
My point in a nutshell. Your name goes on the list, Ban fucking everyone or no one, fines and other assorted Fee's for lists etc should go to the consumers and not for another fucking 600 dollar toilet seat..<br>
